01:32:05,330 --> 01:32:06,540
Warte!

1
01:32:06,620 --> 01:32:10,370
Mein Schatz. Warte!

1
01:32:10,460 --> 01:32:12,460
Gollum, Gollum!

1
01:32:17,510 --> 01:32:19,300
Schnell, schnell!

1
01:32:21,430 --> 01:32:22,720
Tageslicht! Kommt!

1
01:32:25,260 --> 01:32:28,600
- Lauft.
- Kommt schon. Schnell.

1
01:32:31,350 --> 01:32:32,480
Ja, gut!

1
01:34:00,030 --> 01:34:02,190
Beutlin!

1
01:34:02,740 --> 01:34:04,530
Dieb!

1
01:34:05,530 --> 01:34:10,910
Verflucht und zerstückelt!
Wir hassen es auf immerdar!

1
01:34:22,720 --> 01:34:26,220
5, 6, 7, 8.

1
01:34:26,300 --> 01:34:28,640
Bifur. Bofur. Macht 10.

1
01:34:28,720 --> 01:34:30,760
Fili, Kili! Macht 12.

1
01:34:31,520 --> 01:34:34,020
Und Bombur, macht 13.

